# Static Assets

## Background Images (Add these for optimal look)

Place these images in `/static/images/`:

### Recommended Images:
- `hero-bg.jpg` - Ocean/coastal scene (1920x1080+)
- `venue-bg.jpg` - Your venue location or scenic local backdrop
- `rsvp-bg.jpg` - Soft, romantic background
- `wedding-details-bg.jpg` - Elegant pattern or subtle texture

### Size Guidelines:
- Optimize images to < 500KB each
- Use WebP format when possible
- Recommended dimensions: 1920x1080 or 2560x1440

### Free Image Sources:
- Unsplash.com (high-quality free photos)
- Pexels.com (wedding/ocean themes)
- Pixabay.com (royalty-free images)

Search terms: "ocean coastline", "beach wedding", "coastal estate", "elegant wedding"
